rdprofileurl: https://rd.microsoft.com/en-us/suzanne-george
title: The Worlds Most Delicious Cookie
category: sweets and drinks
shortdescription: A true southern United States delight.  This unique cookie is great for all occations.
ingredients: 
1 cup butter
1 cup sugar
1 cup light brown sugar
1 egg
1 cup vegetable oil
1 cup oats (regular)
1 cup crushed cornflakes
3 1/2 cups plain flour
2 tsp vanilla
1 tsp salt
1 tsp soda
1/2 cup flaked coconut
1/2 cup chopped pecans

directions: 
Cream butter and sugars
Add egg, beat well
Add oil and vanilla, mix well
Combine flour, soda, and salt together and then add to creamed mixture.  Mix well
stir in oats, cornflakes, coconut, and nuts.

Shape dough into 1-inch balls and place onto ungreased cookie sheet.  Flatten each one with a fork

Bake at 325 degrees for 12-15 minutes.  cool slightly
remove from cookie sheet and cool on wire racks.
Yield: 10 dozen - small cookies

